Caption.String: The CEC module library indicates this module is bifacial. Check "Module is bifacial" to enable the bifacial model and enter the specifications. See Help for details.
The model assumes a reference bandgap voltage Eg_ref = 1.121 eV, and temperature coefficient for bandgap of -0.0002677 eV/K.
Module unit mass is for the transient thermal model, which automatically applies when the weather file time step is 20 minutes or less. The default value is 11 kg/m².
